	<article id="post-116997" class="post-116997 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail sticky hentry category-live-from-ted2024 category-ted2024 has-thumbnail featured clearfix" role="article">

								<a
				href="https://blog.ted.com/the-ted-theater-at-ted2024-in-photos/"
				class="post-thumbnail"
				style="background-image:url('https://i0.wp.com/blog.ted.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/04/TED2024_20240415_1RL1855-medium.jpg?resize=649%2C487&#038;ssl=1');"
			>
			</a>
				
		<div class="details-wrap">
							<h4>
					<a class="category" href="https://blog.ted.com/category/live-from-ted2024/" data-slug="live-from-ted2024" >
						Live from TED2024					</a>
				</h4>
			
			<h2 class="post-title">
				<a href="https://blog.ted.com/the-ted-theater-at-ted2024-in-photos/" data-slug="the-ted-theater-at-ted2024-in-photos">
					The TED Theater at TED2024, in photos				</a>
			</h2>

			<div class="meta">
				<div class="meta__author">
					<span>By</span> <a href="https://blog.ted.com/author/tedstaff/" title="Posts by TED Staff" class="author url fn" rel="author">TED Staff</a>				</div>
				<div class="meta__date">
					<span>on</span>
					<time datetime="2024-04-18" pubdate >
						Apr 18, 2024					</time>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="excerpt">
								<p>For one incredible week each year, a cavernous wing of the Vancouver Convention Centre in Vancouver, BC, Canada transforms into the TED Theater: a custom-made, hand-built, 1,200-seat theater that plays host to world-changing ideas meant to spark conversation, deepen understanding and drive meaningful change. Below, just a sampling of the incredible photography from this year&#8217;s <a class="read-more" title="Read more" href="https://blog.ted.com/the-ted-theater-at-ted2024-in-photos/">[<span>&hellip;</span>]</a><a class="featured-read-more" href="https://blog.ted.com/the-ted-theater-at-ted2024-in-photos/">Read more</a></p>
							</div>

		</div>

	</article>

