		</h4>
	
	<h2 class="post-title">
		<a href="https://blog.ted.com/bridge-builders-notes-on-session-6-of-ted2024/" data-slug="bridge-builders-notes-on-session-6-of-ted2024">
			Bridge-Builders: Notes on Session 6 of TED2024		</a>
	</h2>

	<div class="meta">
		<div class="meta__author">
			<span>By</span> <a href="https://blog.ted.com/author/marialadias2/" title="Posts by Maria Ladias" class="author url fn" rel="author">Maria Ladias</a>, <a href="https://blog.ted.com/author/oliverfriedman/" title="Posts by Oliver Friedman" class="author url fn" rel="author">Oliver Friedman</a>, <a href="https://blog.ted.com/author/renaereints22/" title="Posts by Renae Reints" class="author url fn" rel="author">Renae Reints</a> and <a href="https://blog.ted.com/author/tom/" title="Posts by Tom Carter" class="author url fn" rel="author">Tom Carter</a>		</div>
		<div class="meta__date">
			<span>on</span>
			<time datetime="2024-04-17" pubdate >
				Apr 17, 2024			</time>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="excerpt">
		<p>In Session 6 of TED2024, we heard from bridge-builders — inspiring speakers working to unite people across political divides, conflicts, differences and more. The event: Talks from Session 6 of TED2024: The Brave and the Brilliant, hosted by TED&#8217;s Helen Walters and Dave Isay, the founder of StoryCorps and winner of the 2015 TED Prize <a class="read-more" title="Read more" href="https://blog.ted.com/bridge-builders-notes-on-session-6-of-ted2024/">[<span>&hellip;</span>]</a></p>
	</div>

</article>			
<article id="post-116771" class="post-116771 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-live-from-ted2024 category-news-2 category-ted2024 tag-alison-taylor tag-andrew-yang tag-avi-loeb tag-bari-weiss tag-bill-ackman tag-scott-galloway tag-ted tag-ted-conferences tag-ted-talks tag-ted2024 tag-xiuhtezcatl has-thumbnail not-featured even i-8 clearfix" role="article">

			<a href="https://blog.ted.com/provocateurs-notes-on-session-5-of-ted2024/" data-slug="provocateurs-notes-on-session-5-of-ted2024" class="post-thumbnail">
			<img src='https://i0.wp.com/blog.ted.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/04/TED2024_20240417_1JR9549.jpg?resize=283%2C212&#038;ssl=1' width='283' height='212' alt='Provocateurs: Notes on Session 5 of TED2024' />		</a>
		
			<h4>
			<a class="category" href="https://blog.ted.com/category/live-from-ted2024/" data-slug="live-from-ted2024" >
				Live from TED2024			</a>
		</h4>
	
	<h2 class="post-title">
		<a href="https://blog.ted.com/provocateurs-notes-on-session-5-of-ted2024/" data-slug="provocateurs-notes-on-session-5-of-ted2024">
			Provocateurs: Notes on Session 5 of TED2024		</a>
	</h2>

	<div class="meta">
		<div class="meta__author">
			<span>By</span> <a href="https://blog.ted.com/author/claytonwickham/" title="Posts by Clayton Wickham" class="author url fn" rel="author">Clayton Wickham</a>, <a href="https://blog.ted.com/author/marialadias2/" title="Posts by Maria Ladias" class="author url fn" rel="author">Maria Ladias</a>, <a href="https://blog.ted.com/author/oliverfriedman/" title="Posts by Oliver Friedman" class="author url fn" rel="author">Oliver Friedman</a> and <a href="https://blog.ted.com/author/renaereints22/" title="Posts by Renae Reints" class="author url fn" rel="author">Renae Reints</a>		</div>
		<div class="meta__date">
			<span>on</span>
			<time datetime="2024-04-17" pubdate >
				Apr 17, 2024			</time>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="excerpt">
		<p>Bold ideas often meet resistance — but what if they were met with curiosity? Session 5 of TED2024 didn’t shy away from audacious ideas. Instead, it invited us all to embrace the discomfort of considering the impossible and unfamiliar, to find the courage to step into someone else’s shoes and assume goodness in those around <a class="read-more" title="Read more" href="https://blog.ted.com/provocateurs-notes-on-session-5-of-ted2024/">[<span>&hellip;</span>]</a></p>
	</div>

</article>			
<article id="post-116891" class="post-116891 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-live-from-ted2024 category-news-2 category-ted2024 tag-cai-guo-qiang tag-ja-collective tag-millie-chu-baird tag-mustafa-suleyman tag-nour-e-rawafi tag-sara-giusto tag-sarah-j-doherty tag-ted tag-ted-conferences tag-ted-talks tag-ted2024 has-thumbnail not-featured odd i-9 clearfix" role="article">

