<article id="post-116781" class="post-116781 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-news-2 category-ted-fellows tag-daro-sulakauri tag-erika-moore-taylor tag-huiyi-lin tag-joel-bervell tag-lehua-kamalu tag-mohamed-aburawi tag-norah-magero tag-paule-joseph tag-ramin-hasani tag-royal-ramey tag-sahba-aminikia tag-ted-fellows tag-ted2024 has-thumbnail not-featured odd i-11 clearfix" role="article">

